standard_question:
在一个多减因养老金模型中，员工可能因退休、死亡或离职而退出计划。已知： 
(1) 年龄 \( x \) 岁的员工在 \( t \) 年内的留存概率 \( {}_{t}p_{x}^{(\tau)} = 1 - 0.03t \), \( 0 \leq t \leq 1 \); 
(2) 退休力 \( \mu_{x+t}^{(1)} = 0.02t \), \( 0 \leq t \leq 1 \); 
(3) 总减因力等于各原因减因力之和。 
试计算退休的中心减因力 \( m_{x}^{(1)} \)。（结果保留5位小数）

对85岁签发的一份保额为1000元的完全离散式生存年金，在生存期间每年初支付生存金，第k年初支付的生存金为 \( \pi_k, k = 0,1,2,\ldots \) ,又已知下列条件: 
(1) \( \pi_k = \pi_0 (1+i)^k \) ; 
(2)生存时间服从De-Moivre规则, \( \omega = \mathbf{110} \) ; 
(3) \( i = 0.05, a_{\overline{30}|} = 15.4 \) ; 
(4)年金现值由等价原理确定。 
试计算 \( \pi_0 \)值为多少。（结果保留1位小数）

In a portfolio of life insurance policies, each policyholder has a probability \( Q \) of death within a year and survives otherwise. \( Q \) varies according to the distribution
\[
F_{Q}(q) = \left\{
\begin{array}{ll}
0 & q \leq 0 \\
3q & 0 < q \leq \frac{1}{4} \\
\frac{1}{2} + q & \frac{1}{4} < q \leq \frac{1}{2} \\
1 & q > \frac{1}{2}
\end{array}
\right.
\]

There are 1000 policyholders with one year of mortality experience. 
Actuary A applies Bühlmann credibility to assign a credibility factor \( Z \) to this experience. Actuary B applies classical credibility to assign a credibility factor \( Z' \), with full credibility assigned if the actual number of deaths is within 10% of the expected number with probability \( p \). It turns out that \( Z = Z' \). Determine \( p \).(The final answer should have 3 decimal places)

A random sample of three claims from an auto insurance plan is given below:
$$
\begin{array}{lll}
\textbf{200} & \textbf{400} & \textbf{450}
\end{array}
$$
Claims are assumed to follow a Pareto distribution with parameters \(\theta = \textbf{100}\) and \(\alpha\).
Determine the maximum likelihood estimate of \(\alpha\).(The final answer should have 4 decimal places.)
